OUR STORY
Blue Heron Restaurant is located within The Great Outdoors Premier RV and Golf Resort in Titusville, Florida. Both our indoor dining room and outdoor dining deck overlook what was voted the
best
golf course
on the Space Coast. Enjoy a variety of dishes from our scratch kitchen, cooked fresh and sourced locally.
Freshness and creativity are our favorite ingredients. Our menu is varied and the service is unmatched. If you’re looking for a superb culinary experience, call us today to make a reservation!
